content: On my S10e I can't bypass the standard navigation keys, resulting in a bright white bar at the bottom of the screen. Also I can't seem to be able to set a new color without having to reset first. And why not realtime preview the new color, now you have to press OK which also closes the colorwheel interface. Refunded and de-instaled
Just what I wanted plus no adds
It's bride enough for my needs.
